{"tid":106474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AlphaGo對柯潔 4月浙江開鑼","createTime":"2017-02-03T16:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T08:31:31.000Z","uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa4c306fa0c3db2e414c31c870fe2af2b0df9c94","tid":106474,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:41:21.000Z","msg":"橫掃圍棋壇的Google人工智能AlphaGo（內地譯：阿爾法狗），將與中國圍棋高手柯潔進行一場終極較量。這是自去年南韓李世石挑戰AlphaGo失敗後「人機大戰」的第二季比賽，日期已經敲定為今年4月，地點是浙江烏鎮。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，人機大戰第二季，也將是人、機最後一戰，柯潔與AlphaGo三番棋大戰後，人類還將組團圍攻AlphaGo，看一看，人類到底能不能贏機器人一次。<br />\n去年3月，代表人類的南韓圍棋高手李世石在五番棋大戰中以1:4負於AlphaGo，說明人工智能在圍棋領域已經超越人類。去年歲末和今年年初，AlphaGo升級版Master在網上又連勝職業高手60盤，包括贏了柯潔三盤。這意味着在快棋領域，人工智能也完勝人類。<br />\n因而，此次人機大戰第二季柯潔與AlphaGo的對弈為慢棋，而且用時比第一季還要長。<br />\n而AlphaGo與柯潔三番棋後，還將接受人類棋手車輪大戰的挑戰，即中日韓各組一隊來挑戰，賽制為類似「廣州世界團體錦標賽」的相談棋形式，即各隊在集體研討之後落子。不過，組隊比賽還未全部落實，中國組隊沒問題，日韓是否接受邀請還未可知。據悉，組隊賽可能採用兩日制用時，即一盤棋對弈一方用時累積可達9小時，通俗地理解，就是說一盤棋要下兩天。<br />\nAlphaGo的研發團隊已表示，第二季結束後，不管結果如何，他們將在人工智能領域終止圍棋的開發。研發團隊的負責人曾表示，他們在人工智能領域開發圍棋項目，一是希望在全世界範圍喚起大眾對圍棋的關注，二是他們開發AlphaGo的目的不是為了跟人類下圍棋，而是希望把開發的成果運用在其他領域。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486084118_9a68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486084118_9a68.jpg&h=76a6f78e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de4f51a59a7b64fd47161a6f600d97c50497322a","tid":106474,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T16:56:05.000Z","msg":"柯潔食蛋無誤<br />\n團戰應該破到蛋"},{"pid":"e52f3150e1b3eb9a365705ef17b2a56e8b461a7e","tid":106474,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>柯潔食蛋無誤<br />\n團戰應該破到蛋</blockquote><br />\n我覺得會全蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAlphaGo已經比上次強好多"},{"pid":"537f92e204ce7a0e06cd96caad456322c120f719","tid":106474,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip alphago 中國人係唔會公平對決的"},{"pid":"c931c0be4fc9e8e1d09fae962e597ab4ec4090e2","tid":106474,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:28:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ae840430b29e5031e3958b380d61d2448f34a5d","tid":106474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip alphago 中國人係唔會公平對決的</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"53f7179a382b3d0d309a908099c9ebe2d319367e","tid":106474,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:38:04.000Z","msg":"玩玩下關晒成場冷氣改關暖氣，熱到你hang機"},{"pid":"9d88ec84a1e43ac6d52383b60e9c0d8fe87b1c37","tid":106474,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩玩下關晒成場冷氣改開暖氣，熱到你hang機</blockquote>"},{"pid":"70da1faaa5d0a8a3b8d576a292f716ec25ff301c","tid":106474,"uid":64621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T21:58:31.000Z","msg":"唔洗估都知AlphaGo輸硬<br />\n支那邊上到Google"},{"pid":"f374f4ed3ff3b9f34979351ca90a780752308294","tid":106474,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T22:46:42.000Z","msg":"事先係儀器裝上360<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766111cc015f52f4117ca57622d6f96f010fcc55","tid":106474,"uid":59782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T22:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事先係儀器裝上360<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhack入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80b245e2f2780f0ae8522b315d3c521347f2bde","tid":106474,"uid":58862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T22:54:25.000Z","msg":"hao123