r />\n柯潔不嬲勁李世石一班啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n李世石當初羸alphago仲未升級都只係羸到1場,而家alphago升左級柯潔想羸到1場已經更難,之前黃博士放alphago上網有同柯潔打連輸幾次,4月再對戰如果食蛋邊度好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdd3fe8c0855c2fd2a473793577a30fef497564","tid":106474,"uid":64621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"柯潔：AlphaGo你連得上Google我當你贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"627767068404c02a5c0c8ec2584657ecb55525e6","tid":106474,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:11:26.000Z","msg":"日本嘅Godmoves表示<br />\n冇人提我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4546883b1fdef76fa8ce77b839848a28639bbaf2","tid":106474,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:19:16.000Z","msg":"之前講過,話有機會係 做神運動<br />\n而家又講到捉完退役<br />\n<br />\n好似有劇本咁<br />\n羸韓仔&gt;再殺盡高手&gt;之後比隻支那狗羸&gt;退役<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電腦既野,都係睇指令<br />\n純粹推測,不喜勿插"},{"pid":"7563142c57ac08b6b9574b52947829a58e401fa4","tid":106474,"uid":36845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"等睇人類食蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}